                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature that slays the deific vessel must succeed at a @Check[will|dc:41] save or be visibly marked as anathema to Asmodeus. It gains weakness 15 to unholy and takes a –2 circumstance penalty to Charisma-based skill checks against followers of Asmodeus. Creatures attempting to [[/act track]] or [[/act gather-information]] about the creature gain a +2 circumstance bonus to their checks. The mark can't be hidden but can be removed by participating in an @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Atone] ritual led by a worshipper of Asmodeus who's 15th level or higher.</p>"
                },
